reviewText: I loved this movie! I watched it flying home from Italy but cannot seem to find a copy available for sale with English subtitles. Would love to buy it when it becomes available to Americans.
Storyline sucks but enjoyed the beautiful designed attire!
One of the most wonderful movies I have ever seen!!!
Go soo is one of my favorites and it was a very interesting movie.
An interesting story of two tailors coming from different points of view.

I waited well over a year to see this. I was not disappointed, it was a wonderful film, although I was terribly frustrated by how long it took to be released with English subtitles in either Region 1 or All Region.
